니다.\\n심장바이오마커 수치가 정상보다 높게 측정되었고 심장초음파상 이첨판의 경미한 변성이 관찰됩니다. 주기적인 검사를 통한 심장질환 진행\\n상태 확인이 필요합니다.\\n소변 검사 결과 요비중이 높고 스트루바이트(struvite)와 칼슘 옥살레이트(calcium oxalate) 성분의 결정이 검출되었습니다. 평소 충분한\\n물을 섭취하도록 하여 결석을 예방해주세요.\\nVaccination\\n구충제\\nNext Date: 2026-07-20\\n차수\\nName\\nDate\\nSign\\n2\\n안텔민 (뽀삐)\\n2026-04-20\\n진료수의사\\nLab Examination\\nDate/Time: 2026-04-20 오후 3:50:00\\nPerformed By [FDC-7000i]\\nName\\nUnit\\nMin\\nMax\\nResult\\nBUN\\nmg/dL\\n9.2\\n29.2\\n20 NORMAL\\nCREA\\nmg/dL\\n0.4\\n1.4\\n0.89 NORMAL\\nBUN/CREA\\n12.5\\n31.8\\n22.5 NORMAL\\nDate/Time: 2026-04-20 오후 3:45:00\\nPerformed By [SOLO]\\nName\\nUnit\\nMin\\nMax\\nResult\\nPancreatic Lipase\\nU/L\\n0\\n125\\n73.7 NORMAL\\nDate/Time: 2026-04-20 오후 3:27:00\\nPerformed By [FDC-7000i]\\nName\\nUnit\\nMin\\nMax\\nResult\\nCRP\\nmg/L\\n0\\n9\\n9 NORMAL\\nDate/Time: 2026-04-20 오후 12:09:52\\nInput By [Manual]\\nName\\nUnit\\nMin\\nMax\\nResult\\nRBC\\n10x6/μL\\n5.5\\n8.5\\n6.80 NORMAL\\nHGB\\ng/dL\\n11\\n19\\n15.7 NORMAL\\nHCT\\n%\\n35\\n56\\n45.5 NORMAL\\nMCV\\nfL\\n57\\n75\\n66.9 NORMAL\\nMCH\\npg\\n20\\n30\\n23.1 NORMAL\\nMCHC\\ng/dL\\n30\\n40\\n34.5 NORMAL\\nRDW-SD\\nfL\\n0.1\\n99.9\\n29.1 NORMAL\\nRDW-CV\\n%\\n13.6\\n21.7\\n13.0 LOW\\nRETIC#\\n10x6/μL\\n0.01\\n0.11\\n0.1115 HIGH\\nRETIC%\\n%\\n0.20\\n1.50\\n1.64 HIGH\\nnRBC#\\nfL\\n0.01\\nIRF\\n%\\n47.3\\nLFR\\n%\\n52.7\\nMFR\\n%\\n16.7\\nHFR\\n%\\n30.6\\nRET-He\\npg\\n23.1\\nPLT\\n10x3/μL\\n148\\n484\\n526 HIGH\\nPDW\\nfL\\n9.9\\nMPV\\nfL\\n0.1\\n30\\n9.2 NORMAL\\nPLT-LCR\\n%\\n0.1\\n99.9\\n19.0 NORMAL\\nPCT\\n%\\n0.14\\n0.46\\n0.48 HIGH\\nWBC\\n10x3/μL\\n5\\n20\\n10.59 NORMAL\\nWBC-NEU#\\n10x3/μL\\n3\\n12\\n7.27 NORMAL\\nWBC-LYM#\\n10x3/μL\\n1\\n6\\n2.22 NORMAL\\nWBC-MONO#\\n10x3/μL\\n0.2\\n1.5\\n0.51 NORMAL\\nWBC-EOS#\\n10x3/μL\\n0.04\\n0.8\\n0.57 NORMAL\\nWBC-BASO#\\n10x3/μL\\n0\\n0.4\\n0.02 NORMAL\\nDate/Time: 2026-04-20 오후 12:07:01\\nInput By [Manual]\\nName\\nUnit\\nMin\\nMax\\nResult\\nSDMA\\nug/dL\\n0\\n14\\n9 NORMAL\\nT4\\nµg/dL\\n1\\n4\\n2.04 NORM